    "description": "Stock up on this cold buster remedy so it’s ready to work its magic when you need it most. Made from fresh ginger, garlic, oranges, and other immunity-boosting ingredients, this easy tonic takes its cold-busting powers even further with antioxidant-rich peppercorns, jalapeños, and habanero peppers. While this concoction has a kick to it, the spice is balanced with cinnamon sticks, rosemary, and other seasonal ingredients that will have you feeling winter fresh.",
